  "description": "Metabolism is the total set of chemical reactions occurring in a living [organism](../../../terms/organism.md). It is what keeps organisms alive — the continuous chemical activity that extracts energy from the environment, builds and maintains cellular structures, and disposes of waste products. An organism that stops metabolizing is dead.",
